### ============================================================================
### Smoke tests — every public + admin GET endpoint against the seeded church.
###
### Base URL: http://localhost:3002/api
### Tenant: the seeded church is resolved via Host header. We send
###   Host: grace_church_dev.localhost   (subdomain == DB name)
### DEFAULT_TENANT in .env is the same slug, so plain `localhost` also works.
###
### Run in VS Code with the "REST Client" extension (send each request), or
### adapt the URL list into curl / the Rust test (tests/smoke.rs) and run
###   cargo test --test smoke
###
### Admin endpoints need a Bearer token. Mint one (HS256, secret = JWT_SECRET)
### or log in via POST /api/auth/login and paste it below.
### ============================================================================

@base = http://localhost:3002/api
@host = grace_church_dev.localhost
@token = <PASTE_ADMIN_JWT_HERE>

### ===================== CONTENT (public) =====================
GET {{base}}/sermons
Host: {{host}}

###
GET {{base}}/sermons/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Host: {{host}}

